nodes.text: Mawshunba Zee was a male Dug who served under Sebolto's employ during the waning years of the Republic Classic era. He also worked for Sesstian Hesser. In 32 BBY, he was wanted by the Galactic Wildlife Liberation Front for the illegal breeding of wild Nexu. The bounty worth 6,000 credits alive and 3,000 dead was claimed by the Mandalorian-turned Bounty hunter Jango Fett.
